headline: Are We on the Verge of a New Normal as Fintechs Pursue Bank Charters?
summary: ALEXANDRIA, Va., October 08, 2025--QED Investors, a leading global fintech venture capital firm, and Oliver Wyman, a global leader in management consulting and a business of Marsh McLennan (NYSE:MMC), today announced a new report titled, Seizing the bank charter moment: Implications for fintechs and banks.
